title: Wishlist Notes need upgrades
text: If I am sharing a wishlist with someone and writing notes in the note field, why can’t the person I’m sharing the list with see it too? Would be a huge upgrade to the app to help communicate between people sharing list in real time

title: Option to review should be more than 14 days
text: The option to write your review should be more than 14 days. Some shady locations wait until the last minute to charge you and then the next day you can’t combat anything or post the review because you have only two weeks to do so!

title: Airbnb site
text: The site was ver easy to navigate.

title: Great customer service!
text: Both my host Cindy and the Airbnb customer service department went above and beyond to help make our reservation process painless. Can’t wait for our family vacation!

title: Good product, bad service
text: Love the listings, customer service can be pretty awful.

title: Casa La Viviana
text: Llevo años trabajando con Airbnb, son confiables, responden rápido a las inquietudes, explican todo correctamente. He incrementado mis ingresos gracias a esta aplicación tan segura.

title: No messaging hosts
text: I am not able to pull up the messages of any hosts that I am currently or have used in the past. Recycled phone and uninstalled/reinstalled app. No good. What can I do?

title: I mostly love this app but needs performance fix.
text: I cannot access messages from my iPhone, the screen is just blank. Even after updating. I need to head to my iPad to see them.
